testcase.name: AppComponent should create the app
AppComponent should have as title 'app'
ArticleComponent should create
ArticlesService should be created
BirthdateDirective should create an instance
LandingComponent should create
LandingService should be created
PasswordDirective should create an instance
MainComponent should create
MainService should be created
ProfileComponent should create
ProfileService should be created
Validate resource actions resource should be a resource (i.e., mock a request)
Validate resource actions resource should give me the http error
Validate resource actions resource should be POSTable
Validate resource actions should update error message (for displaying error mesage to user)
Validate resource actions should update success message (for displaying success message to user)
Validate resource actions should navigate (to profile, main, or landing)
Articles View (component tests) should render articles
Articles View (component tests) should dispatch actions to create a new article
Validate Authentication (involves mocked requests) should log in a user
Validate Authentication (involves mocked requests) should not log in an invalid user
Validate Authentication (involves mocked requests) should log out a user (state should be cleared)
Validate Article actions should fetch articles (mocked request)
Validate Article actions should filter displayed articles by the search keyword
Validate Article actions should update the search keyword
Validate Profile actions (mocked requests) should fetch the user's proile information
Validate Profile actions (mocked requests) should update headline
